| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2021-0491 — Mass File Rename (ransomexx)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 80afa8d0-3a90-503f-8931-fcd871134627"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
